---
title: Rustic Halloumi & Caramelised Onion Burger with Cheesy Spiced Wedges
description: We’re so excited about this burger, with crispy slices of squeaky halloumi, creamy herby mayo and a side of golden potato wedges. Let’s just say, you won’t need the local pub’s menu on hand when you’ve got this recipe under your belt.

